long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension adds a search box to your new tab page, making it easy to find what you're looking for on the web. With our New Tab Search extension, you can add a touch of beauty to your browsing routine every time you open a new tab. 

Search Results are provided by Microsoft Bing.

Using our extension you accept our Privacy and Terms located at:
